TEXT(EV2(<<EOT)); 

The next few problems ask you to compute the inverse of a function \(f\).
Remember that you do this by solving the equation
\(y=f(x)\) for \(x\) and then switching the roles of \(x\) and \(y\).

$BR

Suppose \[f(x) = 2x+4. \]
Then
$BR

\(f^{-1}(x)=\) 
 \{ ans_rule(10) \}.

EOT

ANS(fun_cmp("(x-4)/2", vars=>["x"]));






